JOHANNESBURG - Former Public Enterprises Minister Lynne Brown, Minister Gwede Mantashe and former Deputy Minister Thabang Makwetla are expected to testify at the state capture commission on Friday. Brown will be asked about Eskom while Mantashe and Makwetla will talk about Bosasa. WATCH LIVE: Lynne Brown testifies at Zondo commission  Download the Eyewitness News app to your iOS  or Android  device.